title: CATFISHING: The Facebook Murders
description:
When Jenelle Potter's crush, Billy Payne, started dating another woman, she used Facebook to spread rumors about the couple. But when a CIA agent contacted her parents, informing them that Payne was a threat to Jenelle's life, they took matters into their own hands. This is episode 2 of a special Valentine’s crossover from Crimes of Passion, a Spotify Original from Parcast.
